children.subject: Thanks for sharing! The link is not working though

history.content:
The ASUC Office of Senator Chen has created a newsletter for all things tech, data science, and social good at Berkeley! Every 2 weeks, our office will be compiling a list of updates, events, opportunities, and resources related to the community and sending it out to all relevant clubs and subscribed individuals.

 

Especially during this time, we feel that it’s important to create a space for our communities to share their projects and events - created for students by students :) 

 

Subscribe here! tinyurl.com/asucchen
